3.9.92 - Sep 17, 2013
=====================

Changes since 3.9.91.1:

- Don't mark empty string ("") for translation.
- Use 'virtio-net' in new VM boxes when supported by guest OS.
- Fix network for VM boxes created from gnome-continuous images.
- Fix regression of spinner not getting removed from on top of
  under construction boxes, after import/install was finished.
- Update and adapt to latest libgd.
- Added/updated/fixed translations:
  - Assamese
  - Belarusian
  - Brazilian Portuguese
  - Czech
  - Finnish
  - French
  - German
  - Hebrew
  - Hungarian
  - Indonesian
  - Korean
  - Latvian
  - Norwegian bokmål
  - Punjabi
  - Russian
  - Serbian
  - Slovak
  - Tajik

