=====================

Changes since 3.9.5:

- Adapt to latest govirt and libvirt-gconfig API.
- Fix a typo in user-visible string.
- Added/updated/fixed translations:
  - Brazilian Portuguese
  - Galician
  - Hebrew
  - Lithuanian
  - Norwegian bokmål
  - Russian
  - Slovenian

